VASSAL.build.module.map

Class ForwardToKeyBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.build.module.map.ForwardToKeyBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.util.EventListener, Buildable

    public class ForwardToKeyBuffer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Buildable, java.awt.event.KeyListener
    This KeyListener forwards key event from a Map to the KeyBuffer, where it is given to selected GamePieces to interpret. The event is forwarded only if not consumed
    See Also:
    KeyBuffer, GamePiece.keyEvent(javax.swing.KeyStroke), InputEvent.isConsumed()
